      <title>壳牌与 Equinor 组建英国北海石油天然气合资企业</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/equinor-shell-form-jointly-owned-oil-gas-producer-britain-2024-12-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[壳牌和挪威 Equinor 周四表示，两家公司将合并其在英国北海的资产，组建该盆地最大的石油和天然气公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/equinor-shell-form-jointly-owned-oil-gas-producer-britain-2024-12-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 07:27:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞银称，受美国经济增长推动，全球亿万富翁财富激增</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/global-billionaire-wealth-leaps-fueled-by-us-gains-ubs-says-2024-12-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士银行瑞银周四表示，全球亿万富翁的财富在过去一年里增长了约 17%，其中美国超级富豪的财富大幅增长超过了中国超级富豪财富的下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/global-billionaire-wealth-leaps-fueled-by-us-gains-ubs-says-2024-12-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 07:06:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
